text:
Fifth Avenue, at the NE corner of East 118th Street and eastward to Madison Avenue (right), showing an extension of View No. 1.

The 5-story tenement at the right is No. 1815 Madison Avenue and is located at the N.E. corner of 118th Street.  The latter thoroughfare runs thru the foreground of this view and is obscured by the rocks on the south side of same.

This photo was verified with the photographers successors (N. N. Tiemann & Co., No. 176 Lexington Avenue), and checked with their records of which this is No. 114.

N. N. Tiemann Photo
